1
00:01:09,611 --> 00:01:11,789
Sometimes, I think I'm cursed.

2
00:01:11,904 --> 00:01:14,756
'Cause of something that happened
before I was even born.

3
00:01:15,303 --> 00:01:18,837
See, a long time ago,
there was this family.

4
00:01:19,510 --> 00:01:21,794
The Papá, he was a musician.

5
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:25,184
He and his family
would sing and dance

6
00:01:25,203 --> 00:01:26,537
and count their blessings.

7
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:28,765
But he also had a dream.

8
00:01:29,043 --> 00:01:30,964
To play for the world.

9
00:01:33,364 --> 00:01:34,930
And one day...

10
00:01:35,554 --> 00:01:37,474
he left with his guitar...

11
00:01:38,261 --> 00:01:40,201
and never returned.

12
00:01:47,249 --> 00:01:48,765
And my Mamá...

13
00:01:49,006 --> 00:01:51,925
She didn't have time to cry
over that walk-away musician.

14
00:01:53,777 --> 00:01:56,898
After banishing all music
from her life...

15
00:01:57,858 --> 00:02:00,067
she found a way
to provide for her daughter.

16
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:05,655
She rolled up her sleeves...

17
00:02:05,818 --> 00:02:07,614
and she learned to make shoes.

18
00:02:12,492 --> 00:02:13,941
She could have made candy.

19
00:02:13,961 --> 00:02:15,717
O-o-or fireworks.

20
00:02:16,361 --> 00:02:18,484
Or sparkly underwear for wrestlers.

21
00:02:19,482 --> 00:02:20,998
But no.

22
00:02:21,143 --> 00:02:22,487
She chose shoes.

23
00:02:25,204 --> 00:02:26,999
Then she taught
her daughter to make shoes.

24
00:02:28,488 --> 00:02:30,734
And later, she taught
her son-in-law.

25
00:02:32,156 --> 00:02:33,971
Then her grandkids got roped in.

26
00:02:35,508 --> 00:02:38,081
As her family grew,
so did the business.

27
00:02:39,876 --> 00:02:42,074
Music have torn
her family apart.

28
00:02:43,293 --> 00:02:45,176
But shoes held
them all together.

29
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,613
You see that woman...

30
00:02:48,642 --> 00:02:50,121
