31
00:02:50,140 --> 00:02:51,254
Mamá Imelda.

32
00:02:52,309 --> 00:02:54,499
She died way before I was born.

33
00:02:55,027 --> 00:02:56,968
But my family still
tells her story...

34
00:02:56,996 --> 00:03:00,760
every year on Día de los Muertos
-- the Day of the Dead...

35
00:03:01,634 --> 00:03:05,704
And her little girl?
She's my great-grandmother, Mamá Coco.

36
00:03:05,733 --> 00:03:07,001
Hola, Mamá Coco.

37
00:03:07,693 --> 00:03:10,015
